race.description: Ararat Rural City Council Mdn Plate
race.comment: BURLEIGH (3) resumed from a spell with a narrow defeat over 1100m at Horsham. Bates goes on and will give him a soft ride from an inside gate. In the premier stable, and he's sure to keep improving. Tough to beat. SHAYKHLISLAMOVA (12) was nudged out twice at Mt Gambier and then went to Warrnambool and didn't enjoy the firm track. Goes into the exotics at least at a price. NAITANUI (16) returns from a lay-off. Placed in latest jump-out at Pakenham. Opened last campaign with a second at Geelong over 1125m. In the mix fresh. HOT STEPPING HIPPY (9) returned from a layoff last start and finished sixth over 1200m at Seymour. Can only be fitter and worth including.
